# Cloudflare Pages static redirects (backup).
# www → apex ONLY works after DNS for www exists and www is served by this project.
# Primary fix: Cloudflare Dashboard → DNS → CNAME www → dcalacrity.com (Proxied),
# then Pages → Custom domains → add www.dcalacrity.com (or a Redirect Rule).

https://www.dcalacrity.com/* https://dcalacrity.com/:splat 301
http://www.dcalacrity.com/* https://dcalacrity.com/:splat 301
